# Keep the DockerImageAsset build context minimal so policy-only edits
# rotate the image tag (good), but test/doc edits don't (cheap).
#
# DockerImageAsset content-hashes the entire build context. Including
# .cerbos-tests means every test edit triggers a fresh image push to
# the asset ECR repo + Fargate task rotation. The tests only matter at
# CI time (cerbos compile --tests), not at runtime.
.cerbos-tests/
README.md
build.sh
*.md
